snippet.title: Best VGM 2324 - Dragon Ball Z: Harukanaru Densetsu - Frieza's Ship
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Dragon Ball Z: Harukanaru Densetsu (2007)
Frieza's Ship
Kenji Yamamoto
